race.comment: SONDER (4) comes here in peak condition and proven at the trip. Can race a little closer today after catching the eye late with a handy third over this track and trip. Expected to go close. GLOBAL (9) stretches out to this trip for the first time after his fast finishing fourth over 1800m at the Gold Coast two starts back. Had excuses when seventh at Ipswich. Gets a better set-up and sure to go well. FULMEN FILOU (2) win record hardly excites but the last two runs had merit. Came from near last on the turn with an unlucky second over 2150m at Gunnedah. Will go back again and surge late.  BUSH WARRIOR (8) out of character run when he over-raced throughout and tired badly in the straight when twelfth over 2208m at this track. Assess on earlier efforts.
